{
  "chapter": 5,
  "chapter_summary": "第五回 江上风云\n\n七妙神君（实为辛捷）救出被掳少女后，以绝顶轻功\"暗香浮影\"飞渡长江，将少女安置在自己客栈静室中。少女醒来后回忆身世：父亲方云奇被失散多年的儿子金欹（天魔）所杀，她被金欹掳走后辗转流落至长江水匪船上，最终被辛捷所救。\n\n辛捷与崆峒派于一飞在武汉结交。于一飞提及江面龙王显圣的奇闻，实为辛捷昨夜施展轻功所致。武汉镖头范治成、孟伯起来访，告知七妙神君重现江湖的消息，并提及天魔金欹的残暴行径——一夜灭门八卦游身掌胡大之满门。孟伯起还透露\"海天双煞\"也有重出江湖之意，令辛捷心中一震。\n\n三日后，于一飞在黄鹤楼与武当派约斗。武当派出动掌门首徒凌风剑客和后起之秀神鹤詹平，于一飞以\"少阳九一式\"与詹平激战。雨夜中，一个唱莲花落的怪人出现，扰乱战局。最终于一飞以奇招击败詹平，点其\"将台\"重穴。凌风剑客愤怒离去，双方约定一月后崆峒山上再会。\n\n辛捷成功挑起武当、崆峒两派纷争，暗合梅山民让五大宗派自相残杀的计策。于一飞连夜返回崆峒禀报，辛捷留在黄鹤楼，对莲花落怪人身份心生好奇。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_long_shen",
      "speaker_name": "贺信雄",
      "listener": "char_qi_miao_shen_jun",
      "text": "神君来去匆匆，晚辈也未能一尽仰慕之愿，但望日后有缘，能再睹神君风采，略领教诲。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fang_yun_qi",
      "speaker_name": "方云奇",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不嫁也要嫁。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_yi",
      "speaker_name": "金欹",
      "listener": "char_fang_shi_shao_nv",
      "text": "你不要以为我真拿你没办法，其实我手一点，要你怎样便怎样，只是我实在太喜欢你，不愿意强迫你。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_fang_shi_shao_nv",
      "text": "姑娘，醒来了吗？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_fang_shi_shao_nv",
      "text": "姑娘不必疑心，在下虽是无能，却有一个能为很大的朋友，从船上将姑娘救了下来，姑娘最好还是就在这里静心待一段日子，这里是在下的静室，绝对不会有人来骚扰姑娘。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_yi_fei",
      "speaker_name": "于一飞",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "辛兄怎地起得如此晚？小弟已到前面去溜了一转，而且还听到店伙说起一件奇事。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_yu_yi_fei",
      "text": "小弟怎比得上于兄，今日起来得还算早的了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_yu_yi_fei",
      "text": "于兄所听到的奇事，又是何事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_yi_fei",
      "speaker_name": "于一飞",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "昨夜江岸的几个渔夫，都说见到江心龙王显圣，在水面上来来去去地走，今天一早，就传遍了武汉呢。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_yi_fei",
      "speaker_name": "于一飞",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "依小弟看来，那不过只是有个轻功绝妙的人，在江面施展轻功罢了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_yi_fei",
      "speaker_name": "于一飞",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "只是不知武汉城中传出的此人物，又为何深夜在江面施展轻功？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_yu_yi_fei",
      "text": "若能在江面随意行走，这人的轻功岂非真到了驭气飞行地步了吗？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_yi_fei",
      "speaker_name": "于一飞",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "辛兄还真个以为那人是'随意行走'吗？小弟却看大半是渔夫们的故玄其话罢了，不过总而言之，此人一定是个好手，但突在武汉出现，难道是冲着我于一飞而来的吗？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_yu_yi_fei",
      "text": "于兄太过多虑了，那李治华就是请帮手，也不会有这么快呀！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_yi_fei",
      "speaker_name": "于一飞",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "我倒不是怕他请帮手，只是有点奇怪罢了。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_yu_yi_fei",
      "text": "小弟初到武汉，但于兄久走江湖，想必来得多了，不知可否陪小弟到处走走？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_yi_fei",
      "speaker_name": "于一飞",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "这个自然。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dian_huo",
      "speaker_name": "店伙",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "老爷回来了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dian_huo",
      "speaker_name": "店伙",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "刚才有两位客人来访老爷，一位姓孟，一位姓范，小的认得是城里有名的大镖头，便招待两位进去了，此刻还在里面呢。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_yu_yi_fei",
      "text": "想不到范镖头和孟镖头今日就来回拜了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fan_zhi_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "范治成",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "两位倒真是好雅兴，这么一大早就跑出去逛街，可是到凤林班去了？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_fan_zhi_cheng",
      "text": "范兄休得取笑，倒是令两位久等了，小弟实是不安得很。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_bo_qi",
      "speaker_name": "孟伯起",
      "listener": "char_yu_yi_fei",
      "text": "今日我等前来，除了回拜辛兄之外，还有一件大事要说与于兄知道……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_bo_qi",
      "speaker_name": "孟伯起",
      "listener": "char_yu_yi_fei",
      "text": "那十年前江湖上的奇人'七妙神君'昨晚又突然在武汉现身下。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_yi_fei",
      "speaker_name": "于一飞",
      "listener": "char_meng_bo_qi",
      "text": "这恐怕不可能吧！据家师曾向小弟言及．十年前在五华山里，七妙神君中了家师一掌，又被点苍的掌门人以七绝手法点了两处穴道，焉能活到今日？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_bo_qi",
      "speaker_name": "孟伯起",
      "listener": "char_yu_yi_fei",
      "text": "此话是千真万确，小弟有个挚友，叫江里白龙孙超远，于兄想必也知此人，昨夜就曾亲眼看到七妙神君的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_bo_qi",
      "speaker_name": "孟伯起",
      "listener": "char_yu_yi_fei",
      "text": "孙兄超远今日清晨便来到小弟处，告诉小弟此事，并叫小弟这几日要特别留神，说是眼看江湖中就要生出风波呢。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fan_zhi_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "范治成",
      "listener": "char_meng_bo_qi",
      "text": "其实孟兄弟也是太多虑了，再大的风波，也惹不到你、我的头上，就让他俩拼个胜负，又关你、我甚事？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_fan_zhi_cheng",
      "text": "小弟也曾听说过武林中有个奇人'七妙神君'，武功冠绝天下，却又有何人能与他一拼胜负呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fan_zhi_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "范治成",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "说起此人来，近日江湖上真是谈虎色变，大家只知晓他姓金声名欹，有'天魔'之称，却无人知他师承来历，他出道江湖才只数年，便已做出几件惊人之事，据说非但武功之高，不可思议，而且手段之毒辣，更是匪夷所思，两河中武林的盟主'八卦游身掌胡大之'不知怎地得罪了他，竟被他单人匹马，一夜之间将满门杀得干干净净，当时还有北方知名的剑客'八步赶蝉古尔刚'、'五虎断门刀彭天琪'在场，但这三位赫赫有名的武师，竟未能敌过他一人，全遭了毒手，这次七妙神君夺了他的女子，他岂肯罢休。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_yi_fei",
      "speaker_name": "于一飞",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "想不到昨夜那女子，竟落得七妙神君也动了手。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_yi_fei",
      "speaker_name": "于一飞",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "此次七妙神君重入江湖，倒的确是件大事，小弟待此间事了，便立刻要返回崆峒，禀报家师，天魔金欹和七妙神君的热闹再好看．小弟也无心看了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_bo_qi",
      "speaker_name": "孟伯起",
      "listener": "char_fan_zhi_cheng",
      "text": "武林中平静了将近十年，我就知道必是一场大风暴的前奏，果不其然，乍看江湖中又将是一番腥风血雨，中原五大武林宗派，自身就有了纠纷，现在七妙神君重入江湖，再加上天魔金欹，唉！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fan_zhi_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "范治成",
      "listener": "char_meng_bo_qi",
      "text": "江湖上的混乱尚不止此呢，昔年关中九豪之首，'海天双煞'天残、天废兄弟，据说也静极思动，想重振声威，我们镖局这行饭本已是在刀口上舐血吃，这样一来，这行饭眼看是吃不下去了。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_fan_zhi_cheng",
      "text": "那海天双煞真也要重入江湖吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fan_zhi_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "范治成",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "辛兄对武林人物，怎地知道如此清楚？不过幸好辛兄尚非武林中人，江湖上的风波再大，也不会缠到辛兄头上。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 259
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_yi_fei",
      "speaker_name": "于一飞",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "辛兄何不早些安歇？小弟此去，谅不致有何差错，辛兄放心好了。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_yu_yi_fei",
      "text": "于兄难道不知小弟最是好武，有这等热闹场面，小弟焉有不去之理？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_yi_fei",
      "speaker_name": "于一飞",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "辛兄可去不得，试想辛兄手无缚鸡之力，到了那等凶杀之所，万一小弟一个照料不及，教别人伤了辛兄千金之躯，这天大的担子，小弟万万负不起。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_yu_yi_fei",
      "text": "就是于兄不带小弟去，小弟也要随后赶去的，那些人与小弟无怨无仇，又怎会对小弟如何呢？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_yi_fei",
      "speaker_name": "于一飞",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "辛兄既是执意如此，小弟也无法劝止，只是到时辛兄切记不要乱动，站在一旁看看，也并非不可。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_yu_yi_fei",
      "text": "这个小弟理会得。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_yi_fei",
      "speaker_name": "于一飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "怎么武当门下，还无一人前来，他们的架子，也未免太大了些吧！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_yu_yi_fei",
      "text": "武当派乃居中原武林各派盟座，气派自然不同了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_yu_yi_fei",
      "text": "来了，来了。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_yi_fei",
      "speaker_name": "于一飞",
      "listener": "char_shen_he_zhan_ping",
      "text": "嗳哎，想不到，想不到，于一飞区区一个武林小卒，却劳动了凌风剑客与神鹤詹大侠两位的大驾。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_he_zhan_ping",
      "speaker_name": "神鹤詹平",
      "listener": "char_yu_yi_fei",
      "text": "崆峒三绝剑名满江湖，哪里会将我等武当派放在眼下，在下听李师弟回来一说，虽然明知凭我们这两手三脚猫的剑法，万万不是崆峒剑客的敌手，但我詹某人自不量力，却要来讨教于大侠的高招。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_yi_fei",
      "speaker_name": "于一飞",
      "listener": "char_shen_he_zhan_ping",
      "text": "詹大侠真是太客气了，在下拙于言辞，真不知说什么好，只好在手底下讨教了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_feng_jian_ke",
      "speaker_name": "凌风剑客",
      "listener": "char_yu_yi_fei",
      "text": "于大侠真是快语，这样再好不过了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_feng_jian_ke",
      "speaker_name": "凌风剑客",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "这位是……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_yi_fei",
      "speaker_name": "于一飞",
      "listener": "char_ling_feng_jian_ke",
      "text": "这位是敝友辛捷，久仰武当剑法，特来瞻仰瞻仰的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_zhi_hua",
      "speaker_name": "李治华",
      "listener": "char_ling_feng_jian_ke",
      "text": "这位就是我曾向师兄提及的辛老板。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_he_zhan_ping",
      "speaker_name": "神鹤詹平",
      "listener": "char_yu_yi_fei",
      "text": "那么在下就先领教于大侠几招。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_he_zhan_ping",
      "speaker_name": "神鹤詹平",
      "listener": "char_yu_yi_fei",
      "text": "于大侠倒请了不少帮手。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_yi_fei",
      "speaker_name": "于一飞",
      "listener": "char_shen_he_zhan_ping",
      "text": "于某人虽不成才，却不会找个帮手。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_he_zhan_ping",
      "speaker_name": "神鹤詹平",
      "listener": "char_yu_yi_fei",
      "text": "有请了。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_yi_fei",
      "speaker_name": "于一飞",
      "listener": "char_shen_he_zhan_ping",
      "text": "好剑法。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_feng_jian_ke",
      "speaker_name": "凌风剑客",
      "listener": "char_yu_yi_fei",
      "text": "好，好，崆峒剑客果然好功夫，好手法，武当派今天算是栽在你的手里。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 472,
      "line_end": 474
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_yi_fei",
      "speaker_name": "于一飞",
      "listener": "char_ling_feng_jian_ke",
      "text": "阁下是否也想一试身手？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 476,
      "line_end": 478
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_feng_jian_ke",
      "speaker_name": "凌风剑客",
      "listener": "char_yu_yi_fei",
      "text": "贫道却不会找占便宜的架打，你姓于的身手，贫道迟早总要领教的。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 480,
      "line_end": 482
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_feng_jian_ke",
      "speaker_name": "凌风剑客",
      "listener": "char_li_zhi_hua",
      "text": "还不走？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 486,
      "line_end": 488
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_yi_fei",
      "speaker_name": "于一飞",
      "listener": "char_ling_feng_jian_ke",
      "text": "阁下请转告令师，就说西崆峒的故人，问他十年前的旧物可曾遗落，请令师如约送还崆峒山上。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 490,
      "line_end": 492
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_feng_jian_ke",
      "speaker_name": "凌风剑客",
      "listener": "char_yu_yi_fei",
      "text": "一月之内，家师必定亲至崆峒，请阁下放心好了。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 494,
      "line_end": 496
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_yi_fei",
      "speaker_name": "于一飞",
      "listener": "char_ling_feng_jian_ke",
      "text": "好，好，今秋的泰山之会，还希望阁下也来一显身手。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 498,
      "line_end": 500
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_feng_jian_ke",
      "speaker_name": "凌风剑客",
      "listener": "char_yu_yi_fei",
      "text": "当然。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 502,
      "line_end": 502
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_yu_yi_fei",
      "text": "于兄果然剑法绝伦，今日小弟真开了眼界。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 508,
      "line_end": 510
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_fan_zhi_cheng",
      "text": "今日小弟作东，在那凤林班里请各位喝酒为于兄庆功，各位可赞成？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 512,
      "line_end": 514
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_yi_fei",
      "speaker_name": "于一飞",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "辛兄的好意，小弟心领了，小弟必须连夜回崆峒，向家师禀明此事。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 516,
      "line_end": 518
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_yi_fei",
      "speaker_name": "于一飞",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "还有那'七妙神君'重现江湖，小弟也要立刻禀明家师作个准备。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 520,
      "line_end": 522
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_yu_yi_fei",
      "text": "于兄如有正事，小弟自是不能相强，但今日一别，后会无期，小弟却难过得很。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 524,
      "line_end": 526
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_yi_fei",
      "speaker_name": "于一飞",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "小弟孑然一身，来去自如，只待事了，小弟必再来此间，与各位尽十日之欢，今日就此别过了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 528,
      "line_end": 530
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fan_zhi_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "范治成",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "辛兄可认识那人吗？",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 534,
      "line_end": 536
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_fan_zhi_cheng",
      "text": "不认得。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 538,
      "line_end": 538
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_bo_qi",
      "speaker_name": "孟伯起",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "雨中不是谈话之处，辛兄不如与小弟们一起坐船渡江吧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 542,
      "line_end": 544
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xin_jie",
      "speaker_name": "辛捷",
      "listener": "char_meng_bo_qi",
      "text": "小弟最是好奇，还想留在此地，范兄、孟兄先请回吧！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 546,
      "line_end": 548
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fan_zhi_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "范治成",
      "listener": "char_xin_jie",
      "text": "这样也好，说不定辛兄还有奇遇，只是小弟们却要先走一步。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 550,
      "line_end": 552
    }
